{"type": "article", "id": 15291, "title": "要让餐厅让人印象深刻，入口可以赢一半颜值分", "description": "一个雕塑，就给餐厅增添了活力。", "date": "2015-09-23T08:24:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5133, "name": "西班牙"}, {"id": 4814, "name": "餐厅设计"}, {"id": 5798, "name": "艺术装置"}, {"id": 16390, "name": "木结构"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071050485kCy9TcogsKnSDJM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t最近，<a href=\"http://www.tamatestudio.com\" target=\"_blank\">建筑事务所 tamatestudio </a>为一家西班牙餐厅<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\">打造了一个流线型、木结构的入口。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071050426DXjB1Kvz4mGHJOr.jpg\" title=\"这个餐厅位于西班牙的 Alicante\" alt=\"这个餐厅位于西班牙的 Alicante\" data-ratio=\"0.4578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a><span>这个餐厅位于西班牙的 Alicante</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105043T8X152tWovO0Eref.jpg\" title=\"远远望去，它还挺显眼的\" alt=\"远远望去，它还挺显眼的\" data-ratio=\"0.4609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a><span>远远望去，还挺显眼的</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105043PBSH7ehV1xCngYjk.jpg\" title=\"后面彩色的现代部分是餐厅\" alt=\"后面彩色的现代部分是餐厅\" data-ratio=\"0.9453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a><span>后面彩色的现代部分是餐厅</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105044BAhWV45qpGcS0Pnz.jpg\" title=\"傍晚时分\" alt=\"傍晚时分\" data-ratio=\"0.8015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a><span>傍晚时分</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105044pGiLfY9myPJTExte.jpg\" title=\"夜晚\" alt=\"夜晚\" data-ratio=\"0.4765625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a><span>夜晚</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105044hoBaCiPs74Nrq1mn.jpg\" title=\"大体量\" alt=\"大体量\" data-ratio=\"1.128125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a><span>大体量</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105045wAgFh7eU19GJaM5b.jpg\" title=\"从内部看\" alt=\"从内部看\" data-ratio=\"0.6265625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a><span>从内部看</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071050453nl70tsXcGJoj5kF.jpg\" title=\"细节\" alt=\"细节\" data-ratio=\"0.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a><span>细节</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105046qXa01FpczWjyMuQw.jpg\" title=\"人的比例\" alt=\"人的比例\" data-ratio=\"0.215625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a><span>人的比例</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t虽然不防水，但这个木结构的装置为餐厅增添了活力。<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"http://www.tamatestudio.com\" target=\"_blank\">建筑事务所 tamatestudio </a>还参与了许多项目的设计，以下是他们的部分作品：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105046bimLA3pN4UFQBl6j.jpg\" title=\"店铺设计\" alt=\"店铺设计\" data-ratio=\"0.6578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a><span>店铺设计</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105046juMkBgz6ITCOZYlh.jpg\" title=\"餐厅设计\" alt=\"餐厅设计\" data-ratio=\"1.4421875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a>餐厅设计，风格很浓郁\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105047gCRn0vb1ia4KGtyo.jpg\" title=\"住宅设计\" alt=\"住宅设计\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a>住宅设计\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105047NBJyqGYTEh2deRpM.jpg\" title=\"店铺设计\" alt=\"店铺设计\" data-ratio=\"1.4609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a>店铺设计\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/09/21/a-sculptural-wood-entrance-greets-you-at-this-restaurant-and-bar-in-spain/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>contemporist</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}